This is a basic toolchain to help develop games made in Honeycomb.

Once compiled, put the binaries in a separate Honeycomb package and place honeycomb.bat next to all other packages. (You can find honeycomb.bat in this repository)

Current commands:
./honeycomb build [package name] - Build a specific package and copy all assets over
./honeycomb buildall - Build all packages and copy every asset over
./honeycomb clean [package name] - Literally just "dotnet clean"
./honeycomb cleanall - Runs "dotnet clean" for all packages
./honeycomb play - Build _CORE package and runs it.
./honeycomb sync [package name] - Copy all assets over
./honeycomb syncall - Copy every asset over